#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:37
msgid "Number of epochs to run and train agent."
msgstr "執行和訓練代理程式的訓練週期數。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:39
msgid "Maximum length of replay buffer."
msgstr "經驗回放緩衝區 (Replay Buffer) 的最大長度。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:41
msgid "Discount factor. (Always between 0 and 1.)"
msgstr "折扣因子 (Discount Factor)。（始終介於 0 和 1 之間。）"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:43
msgid ""
"Interpolation factor in polyak averaging for target networks. Target "
"networks are updated towards main networks according to:  .. math:: "
"\\theta_{\\text{targ}} \\leftarrow     \\rho \\theta_{\\text{targ}} + "
"(1-\\rho) \\theta  where :math:`\\rho` is polyak. (Always between 0 and "
"1, usually close to 1.)"
msgstr ""

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:43
msgid ""
"Interpolation factor in polyak averaging for target networks. Target "
"networks are updated towards main networks according to:"
msgstr "目標網路 Polyak 平均的內插因子。目標網路根據以下公式向主網路更新："

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:47
msgid ""
"\\theta_{\\text{targ}} \\leftarrow\n"
"\\rho \\theta_{\\text{targ}} + (1-\\rho) \\theta\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:50
msgid ""
"where :math:`\\rho` is polyak. (Always between 0 and 1, usually close to "
"1.)"
msgstr "其中 :math:`\\rho` 是 polyak。（始終介於 0 和 1 之間，通常接近 1。）"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:53
msgid "Learning rate for policy."
msgstr "策略的學習率。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:55
msgid "Learning rate for Q-networks."
msgstr "Q 網路的學習率。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:57
msgid "Minibatch size for SGD."
msgstr "SGD 的小批次大小。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:59
msgid ""
"Number of steps for uniform-random action selection, before running real "
"policy. Helps exploration."
msgstr "在執行真正策略之前，均勻隨機動作選擇的步數。有助於探索。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:62
msgid ""
"Number of env interactions to collect before starting to do gradient "
"descent updates. Ensures replay buffer is full enough for useful updates."
msgstr ""
"在開始進行梯度下降更新之前要收集的環境互動次數。確保回放緩衝區有足夠的資料以"
"進行有效的更新。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:66
msgid ""
"Number of env interactions that should elapse between gradient descent "
"updates. Note: Regardless of how long you wait between updates, the ratio"
" of env steps to gradient steps is locked to 1."
msgstr ""
"梯度下降更新之間應經過的環境互動次數。注意：無論更新之間等待多久，環境步數與"
"梯度步數的比率鎖定為 1。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:71
msgid ""
"Stddev for Gaussian exploration noise added to policy at training time. "
"(At test time, no noise is added.)"
msgstr "訓練時添加到策略的高斯探索雜訊的標準差。（測試時不添加雜訊。）"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:74
msgid "Stddev for smoothing noise added to target policy."
msgstr "添加到目標策略的平滑化雜訊的標準差。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:77
msgid "Limit for absolute value of target policy smoothing noise."
msgstr "目標策略平滑化雜訊絕對值的上限。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:80
msgid ""
"Policy will only be updated once every policy_delay times for each update"
" of the Q-networks."
msgstr "策略僅在每 policy_delay 次 Q 網路更新時才更新一次。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:83
msgid ""
"Number of episodes to test the deterministic policy at the end of each "
"epoch."
msgstr "每個訓練週期結束時測試確定性策略的回合數。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:86
msgid "Maximum length of trajectory / episode / rollout."
msgstr "軌跡／回合／展開的最大長度。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:88
msgid "Keyword args for EpochLogger."
msgstr "EpochLogger 的關鍵字引數。"

#: of spinup.algos.pytorch.td3.td3.td3:90
msgid ""
"How often (in terms of gap between epochs) to save the current policy and"
" value function."
msgstr "儲存當前策略和價值函數的頻率（以訓練週期之間的間隔表示）。"

#: ../../algorithms/td3.rst:154
msgid "Saved Model Contents: PyTorch Version"
msgstr "儲存的模型內容：PyTorch 版本"

#: ../../algorithms/td3.rst:156
msgid ""
"The PyTorch saved model can be loaded with ``ac = "
"torch.load('path/to/model.pt')``, yielding an actor-critic object "
"(``ac``) that has the properties described in the docstring for "
"``td3_pytorch``."
msgstr ""
"PyTorch 儲存的模型可透過 ``ac = torch.load('path/to/model.pt')`` 載入，"
"會得到一個演員-評論家 (Actor-Critic) 物件（``ac``），具有 ``td3_pytorch`` "
"文件字串中描述的屬性。"

